sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant AdminPanel
    participant Backend
    participant Database
    participant FileSystem

    %% Admin Add Food Item
    Note over Admin,Database: Admin - Add Food Item Flow
    Admin->>AdminPanel: Navigate to Add page
    Admin->>AdminPanel: Fill food details & upload image
    Admin->>AdminPanel: Submit form
    AdminPanel->>Backend: POST /api/food/add (FormData)
    Backend->>Backend: Multer processes image
    Backend->>FileSystem: Save image to uploads/
    FileSystem-->>Backend: Image saved
    Backend->>Database: Create food document
    Database-->>Backend: Food created
    Backend-->>AdminPanel: Success response
    AdminPanel-->>Admin: Show success notification

    %% Admin View Food List
    Note over Admin,Database: Admin - View Food List Flow
    Admin->>AdminPanel: Navigate to List page
    AdminPanel->>Backend: GET /api/food/list
    Backend->>Database: Fetch all food items
    Database-->>Backend: Food items array
    Backend-->>AdminPanel: Return food list
    AdminPanel-->>Admin: Display food table

    %% Admin Delete Food Item
    Note over Admin,FileSystem: Admin - Delete Food Item Flow
    Admin->>AdminPanel: Click delete on item
    AdminPanel->>Backend: POST /api/food/remove {id}
    Backend->>Database: Find food by id
    Database-->>Backend: Food data
    Backend->>FileSystem: Delete image from uploads/
    FileSystem-->>Backend: Image deleted
    Backend->>Database: Delete food document
    Database-->>Backend: Food deleted
    Backend-->>AdminPanel: Success response
    AdminPanel->>Backend: GET /api/food/list (refresh)
    Backend->>Database: Fetch updated list
    Database-->>Backend: Updated food items
    Backend-->>AdminPanel: Return updated list
    AdminPanel-->>Admin: Display updated table
